Mach number (non-dim): 0.0190914
Reynolds number (per m): 444982
Initial pressure (non-dim): 0
Initial density (non-dim): 1
Initial velocity (non-dim): (1, 0, 0). Magnitude: 1
Initial viscosity (non-dim): 2.24728e-06


